    <item>
      <title>《教父》和《现代启示录》演员罗伯特·杜瓦尔去世，享年 95 岁</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/16/movies/robert-duvall-dead.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为奥斯卡奖得主，他因在《现代启示录》和《教父》等电影以及电视连续剧《孤独的鸽子》中扮演各种角色而闻名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/16/movies/robert-duvall-dead.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Feb 2026 21:26:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
